{"tid":712803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[音速爆炸] 【內地正研發超音速的高鐵】","createTime":"2018-06-22T11:29:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T12:21:14.000Z","uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"afcac70f62ebeea563b8a3e2d5e2cbe85703df64","tid":712803,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"【內地正研發超音速的高鐵】<br />\n【料2021年投入試驗】<br />\n<br />\n法拉利最快可達350公里，日本的磁懸浮列車時速603公里，已經是列車中的世界紀錄保持者。不過，內地近日指要打破以上紀錄，已著手研發時速1500公里的超級高鐵，勢要挑戰超音速。<br />\n<br />\n時速1500公里是怎樣的概念呢？內地高鐵目前最高設計時速是380公里；我們平時乘搭的民航客機，是時速800到1000公里；就算音速都是時速1200公里。<br />\n<br />\n公布這個消息的西南交通大學首席教授張衛華和他的團隊，已經在大學搭建了一條全長45米的真空環形軌道，由駕駛員操作這架單人車進行試驗。<br />\n<br />\n張衛華介紹，超級高鐵採用高溫超導磁懸浮和真空管技術，理論上是可以達到時速1500公里，預計2021年可以正式試驗。<br />\n<br />\n不過研究高鐵的學者紀嘉倫反駁，在理論上，半真空下可達到時速一千公里，全真空甚至可達時速一萬公里，不過離實踐還很遠。「首先要搞實驗一個大規模的真空，如果搞一小管的真空還容易，但搞一個大管的真空，還要人在裡面要有空氣，非常難的，得多大成本，還不如坐飛機呢。」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，美國有公司亦曾經用同一項技術做過試驗，結果時速只有387公里。<br />\n<br />\n#超級高鐵<br />\n#超越音速<br />\n#厲害了我的國<br />\n#就快追得上戰機<br />\n#如果試驗成功大家想睇邊個去開幕試坐<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1755027087975103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F1755027087975103%2F&d=YiWMfvDEND4MnMFLKsmhCjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=92c6a35a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/1755027087975103/</a><br />\n<br />\n邊行邊爆不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d62f4149a5d3a7f11a0034e6bac0cda33675801","tid":712803,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:39:51.000Z","msg":"咁高鐵幾時拆？"},{"pid":"a21c8acefb0e08ba09d115850bfd7adabcc32878","tid":712803,"uid":31017,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:45:23.000Z","msg":"人有幾大膽，車就有幾快<br />\n大陸有超光速列車，直入冥河都唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03be6ec76e1abaccc3161a025d7dd8f96dc0c1e","tid":712803,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"下次挑戰光速<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48fb981f2e6112f6cad0471583489fcd4fd03fa","tid":712803,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"雷聲大雨點小<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11f0015fb040c2a4a9ff02428b9a24244ad8b37","tid":712803,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"用1秒333米嘅速度，行45米嘅隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157780991601f7c6a631f2d8bcf856678fdc512d","tid":712803,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11f0015fb040c2a4a9ff02428b9a24244ad8b37","tid":712803,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"用1秒333米嘅速度，行45米嘅隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你"},{"pid":"c6e1ed36100622077daecf5c35880f3d4971f637","tid":712803,"uid":63163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f11f0015fb040c2a4a9ff02428b9a24244ad8b37","tid":712803,"uid":44454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"用1秒333米嘅速度，行45米嘅隧道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T12:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 環型隧道, 仲話有駕駛員, 真係好撚癲"},{"pid":"6cd5034d5d72f6b2d8790a49ea93ed650e9422b0","tid":712803,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6e1ed36100622077